        <ul>
            <li>Spotify and Apple Deezer Streaming</li>
            <li>Beautiful Colorflow-inspired album and now-playing views</li>
            <li>Branded Spotify and Deezer UI</li>
            <li>Search for tracks, albums or artists</li>
        </ul>
        <h2>Choose between Spotify and Deezer</h2>
        <div class="flex-row half">
            <img src="https://www.scdn.co/i/_global/open-graph-default.png" alt="Spotify Banner" onclick="window.location.href = '/spotify'">
